subfinder -d example.com -silent > subs.txt
subfinder -d example.com -silent \
&& amass enum -passive -d example.com -silent >> subs.txt

Filter Live Subdomains (THIS IS KEY)
Use httpx (industry standard)
cat subs.txt | httpx -silent -threads 100 > live.txt



One-Liner (Enumeration â†’ Live Only)

If you want speed over perfection:

subfinder -d example.com -silent | httpx -silent > live.txt


ADVANCED FILTERING (Highly Recommended)
Filter only interesting status codes
httpx -status-code -silent | grep -E "200|301|302|403"

Include title + tech fingerprinting
httpx -title -tech-detect -silent

Save JSON for automation
httpx -json -silent > live.json
